<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
    	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
		<title>公告通知详情</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/api.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/commonWindow.css" />
		<style type="text/css">
			body{
				min-width: 320px;
                background: #F8F8F8;
			}
            #main{
                width:100%;
                padding:12px 8px 0px;
                box-sizing: border-box;
            }
            .preview_body{
                width:100%;
                padding:12px;
                box-sizing: border-box;
                background: #FFFFFF;
                box-shadow: 0 2px 4px 0 #CDE3E9;
                border-radius: 4px;
            }
            .title{
                width:100%;
                text-align: center;
                font-size:16px;
                color:#333333;
                line-height:22px;
                overflow: hidden;
                text-overflow: ellipsis;
                white-space: nowrap;
            }
            .text_info{
                width:100%;
                margin-top:6px;
                line-height:20px;
                font-size:14px;
                color:#333333;
                letter-spacing: 0.9px;
                text-align: justify;
                text-indent: 2em;
            }
            .img_info{
                width:100%;
            }
            .img_info li{
                width:100%;
                height:130px;
                border-radius:8px;
                box-sizing: border-box;
                overflow: hidden;
                margin-bottom:6px;
            }
            .img_info>:nth-child(1){
                margin-top:6px;
            }
            .img_info li>img{
                width:100%;
                height:100%;
            }
            .bottom_tag{
                width:100%;
                overflow: hidden;
            }
            .bottom_tag>:nth-child(1),.bottom_tag>:nth-child(2){
                font-size:12px;
                color:#666666;
                float:left;
            }
            .bottom_tag>:nth-child(1){
                margin-right:6px;
            }
            .bottom_tag>:nth-child(3){
                font-size:12px;
                color:#BDBDBD;
                float:right;
            }
            .notice_detail{
                width:100%;
                background: #FFFFFF;
                margin-top:12px;
                box-shadow: 0 2px 4px 0 #CDE3E9;
                border-radius: 4px;
                padding:12px 12px 0px;
                box-sizing: border-box;
            }
            .top_bar{
                width:100%;
                overflow: hidden;
            }
            .top_bar>:nth-child(1){
                font-size: 14px;
                color: #333333;
                line-height:20px;
                float:left;
                padding-top:4px;
                margin-right:20px;
            }
            .top_bar>:nth-child(2),.top_bar>:nth-child(3){
                float:left;
                height:24px;
                padding-left:10px;
                padding-right:10px;
                line-height:24px;
                font-size:12px;
                color:#999999;
                background: #F2F2F2;
                border-radius:100px;
                box-sizing: border-box;
            }
            .top_bar>:nth-child(2){
                margin-right:12px;
            }
            .top_bar .selected{
                background: #5AC8E1;
                color:#fff;
            }
            .notice_table{
                width:100%;
            }
            .notice_table>table{
                width:100%;
                margin-top:12px;
            }
            thead>tr{
                width:100%;
                height:44px;
                background: #EBFBFF;
                border-radius: 4px;
                box-sizing: border-box;
            }
            th{
                width:33.33%;
                font-weight:normal;
                font-size: 14px;
                color: #333333;
                letter-spacing: 0.19px;
            }
            tbody tr{
                width:100%;
                height:41px;
                border-bottom: 1px solid #F2F2F2;
            }
            tbody tr td{
                width:33.33%;
                text-align: center;
                font-size: 12px;
                color: #333333;
            }
            tbody tr>:nth-child(3){
                color:#999999
            }
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
        <div id="main">
            <div class="preview_body">
                <div class="title">
                    我眼中的万花筒幼儿园
                </div>
                <div class="text_info">
                    我眼中的万花筒幼儿园，除了那建筑外墙的绿色给了我一种充满活力的森林感觉外，更主要的是万花筒幼儿园的老师们给我这个初为人父的感觉和一种无法用文字来言表的信赖。孔子说过“性相近，习相远也”，由此可见一个良好习惯的养成是从吖吖学语、幼儿教育开始的。
                </div>
                <ul class="img_info">
                    <li>
                        <img src="../../image/wonderful03.png" alt="">
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <div class="bottom_tag">
                    <span>需要签收</span>
                    <span>可以分享</span>
                    <span>李老师分享于<em>2018.02.31</em>
                    <em>12:30</em></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="notice_detail">
                <div class="top_bar">
                    <div><span>全部投放</span><span>(6)</span></div>
                    <div class="selected"><span>已签收</span><span>(2)</span></div>
                    <div><span>未签收</span><span>(4)</span></div>
                </div>
                <div class="notice_table">
                    <table>
                        <thead>
                            <tr>
                                <th>宝宝姓名</th>
                                <th>家长姓名</th>
                                <th>确认时间</th>
                            </tr>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>孔明</td>
                                    <td>孔亮</td>
                                    <td>2018.02.08 12:30</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>孔明</td>
                                    <td>孔亮</td>
                                    <td>2018.02.08 12:30</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>孔明</td>
                                    <td>孔亮</td>
                                    <td>2018.02.08 12:30</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>孔明</td>
                                    <td>孔亮</td>
                                    <td>2018.02.08 12:30</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>孔明</td>
                                    <td>孔亮</td>
                                    <td>2018.02.08 12:30</td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </thead>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
	</body>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/api.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/util.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/kv.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/apiCloud.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/public.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/template-native.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/data.js"></script>
</html>
